{"arkId":"cl010104852","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010104852","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre ronde assortie d\u0027une ch\u00e2telaine","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre ronde assortie d\u0027une ch\u00e2telaine"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XV (1715-1774) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1767 - 1768","currentLocation":"Sully, [OArt] Salle 614 - Galerie Louis XV, Vitrine 7","room":"Salle 614, Aile Aile Sully, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1767,"endYear":1768,"imprecision":"","text":"3e quart du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Archambo, John","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""},{"label":"Hunt, James","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Orf\u00e8vre","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 8390","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Bo\u00eetier en or orn\u00e9 d\u0027un m\u00e9daillon rocaille repr\u00e9sentant Apollon jouant de la lyre entour\u00e9 de trois Muses dans un d\u00e9cor d\u0027architectures, entour\u00e9 de rinceaux d\u00e9coup\u00e9s \u00e0 jour. Lunette du verre repouss\u00e9e de motifs rocailles s\u00e9par\u00e9s par des rinceaux grav\u00e9s et reperc\u00e9s, t\u00eate du pendant grav\u00e9e d\u0027une rosace. Poussoir enrichi d\u0027un diamant, charni\u00e8re moulur\u00e9e. Cadran \u00e0 chiffres romains et arabes, aiguilles orn\u00e9es de roses de diamant. Mouvement muni d\u0027une r\u00e9p\u00e9tition, un carillon \u00e0 six timbres jouant un air dont le titre est inscrit sur la rosette de r\u00e9glage : Mirleton-Trumpet tune. Echappement \u00e0 roue de rencontre. Coq \u00e0 deux pieds ajour\u00e9 de rinceaux o\u00f9 apparaissent deux t\u00eates de dauphins. Ch\u00e2telaine \u00e0 quatre plaques orn\u00e9es de diverses figures : Mars ex\u00e9cutant le portrait de V\u00e9nus (repr\u00e9sentant la Peinture), un buste de femme tenant un marteau et une \u00e9querre (la Sculpture), une femme pr\u00e8s d\u0027un livre ouvert et un amour avec un livre. Quatre breloques sont suspendues : deux oeufs d\u00e9cor\u00e9s de fleurs, un cachet figurant la t\u00eate de Mercure et une cassolette \u00e0 parfum.","inscriptions":"Poin\u00e7on : \r ; t\u00eate de l\u00e9opard ; lettre-date, Londres, 1767-1768 ; lion passant ; ma\u00eetre, James Hunt\r ; Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : Archambo LONDON N 1650","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"22","displayDimension":"22 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"5,7","displayDimension":"5,7 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"3,8","displayDimension":"3,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Longueur","value":"15","displayDimension":"15 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":4,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : or\r\nTechnique : \u00e9maill\u00e9 = \u00e9maillage = \u00e9mail = \u00e9maux (techniques m\u00e9tal)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : diamant\r\nTechnique : techniques m\u00e9tal (orf\u00e8vrerie)","placeOfCreation":"Londres (Grande-Bretagne = Grande Bretagne-\u003EAngleterre)","dateOfDiscovery"